\section*{AHEP Learning Outcomes Assessed}
This assignment assesses the following AHEP Learning Outcomes:
\begin{itemize}
    \item \textbf{M1:} Apply knowledge of mathematics, statistics, natural science, and engineering principles to complex problems.
    \item \textbf{M2:} Formulate and analyze complex problems to reach substantiated conclusions.
    \item \textbf{M3:} Select and apply computational and analytical techniques to model complex problems, considering their limitations.
\end{itemize}

